summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3496 for the improvement of The Alley in Block 8, Green's Addition, being the Alley between Yale Avenue North and Eastlake Avenue, from East Boston Street to Easy Lynn Street; all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 43321, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
